                        <a class="term" href="#vothG_fuehrer">fuehrer</a> because there was a <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> in that village, but neither the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>
                        <a class="term" href="#vothG_fuehrer">fuehrer</a> nor the mayor would take us in. We sat on the street with the little belongings that we still had. We were all wet. It poured, but still our pleading was of no avail, and since I was the senior among them I had to go plead everywhere while the whole party sat on the street and wept[here she herself weeps] </span>
